section.sec-banner
  .container
    .sec-banner__content
      div(class="md:hidden relative text-[44px] z-2 mt-[50px]")
        div(class="font-black italic text-center uppercase leading-[110%]") Сеть клубов #[br] #[span(class="text-app-accent") гоночных #[br] симуляторов]
        img(class="md:hidden absolute right-[-5%] z-1 w-[110%] object-cover" src="./img/banner-bg-mob.png" alt="" style="max-width: none;")

      div(class="sec-banner__contacts z-2 mt-auto flex gap-2.5 max-md:flex-col max-md:items-center max-md:gap-5")
        div(class="sec-banner__contacts-socs max-md:order-3 flex  items-center gap-1.5 max-md:w-full max-md:justify-center max-md:text-center")
          a(href="#").btn.btn-icon-white
            img(class="img-base" src="./img/accent-whatsapp.svg", alt="")
            img(class="img-hover" src="./img/hover-whatsapp.svg", alt="")
          a(href="#").btn.btn-icon-white
            img(class="img-base" src="./img/accent-tg.svg", alt="")
            img(class="img-hover" src="./img/hover-tg.svg", alt="")
          a(href="#").btn.btn-icon-white
            img(class="img-base" src="./img/accent-vk.svg", alt="")
            img(class="img-hover" src="./img/hover-vk.svg", alt="")
        
        div(class="md:hidden w-full")
          button(class="btn-accent order-2 mx-auto w-full max-w-[337px] h-[63px]") Онлайн-запись

        div(class="flex max-md:flex-wrap max-md:justify-center z-2 gap-[15px] max-md:order-1 text-[24px] max-lg:text-sm max-md:text-base font-bold uppercase ml-auto max-md:ml-0")
          div(class="sec-banner__contacts-address")
            p МОСКВа (#[span.text-c-accent new])
            p Санкт-петербург

          div(class="sec-banner__contacts-phones flex flex-col")
            a(href="tel:" class="sec-banner__contacts-phone hover:text-app-pink") #[span(class="text-app-pink") +] 7 812 665-38-88
            a(href="tel:" class="sec-banner__contacts-phone hover:text-app-pink") #[span(class="text-app-pink") +] 7 812 565-38-88

      div(class="mt-[32px] py-4 flex flex-wrap justify-between border-top border-app-white-secondary gap-2.5 text-[19px] max-md:p-0 max-md:justify-center max-md:mt-5 text-app-white-secondary max-md:text-center max-md:text-sm font-golos font-medium  z-2")
        div(class="max-md:hidden flex gap-2 items-center")
          img(src="./img/14+.svg", alt="")
          p Погрузись в атмосферу — почувствуй настоящую гонку <br/> и прокачай навыки управления автомобилем.
        .sec-banner__desc-worktime Ежедневно с 12:00 до 00:00 <br/> Отвечаем моментально.


